  "<button id=\"saveBtn\" type=\"button\" title=\"存檔／讀檔（存在這台裝置·可匯出成檔案）\">💾 存讀檔</button>": "<button id=\"saveBtn\" type=\"button\" title=\"Save / load (kept on this device, exportable to a file)\">💾 Save</button>",
  "<button id=\"toolsBtn\" type=\"button\" title=\"除錯工具（除錯／擂台／地圖）\">🔧</button>": "<button id=\"toolsBtn\" type=\"button\" title=\"Tools: map, opponent, save\">🔧</button>",
  "<div class=\"pTitle\">⚔️ 擂台·測試對戰</div>": "<div class=\"pTitle\">⚔️ Arena — test battles</div>",
  "<div class=\"abHead\"><span>自訂兵力</span><span class=\"abLR\">左隊 ／ 右隊</span></div>": "<div class=\"abHead\"><span>Custom armies</span><span class=\"abLR\">left / right</span></div>",
  "<div class=\"arenaRow\"><button id=\"arenaGo\" type=\"button\">▶ 開打</button><button id=\"arenaReplay\" type=\"button\">↻ 重開</button><button id=\"arenaExit\" type=\"button\">✕ 離開</button></div>": "<div class=\"arenaRow\"><button id=\"arenaGo\" type=\"button\">▶ Fight</button><button id=\"arenaReplay\" type=\"button\">↻ Rerun</button><button id=\"arenaExit\" type=\"button\">✕ Exit</button></div>",
  "<div class=\"arenaHint\">點預設＝直接開打；或自訂左右兵數再「開打」。左隊＝你（下方標籤切 攻擊/守備×集中/相剋/打帶跑·可拖單兵）。重開＝同組再來看機率波動。離開＝重載回正常遊戲。</div>": "<div class=\"arenaHint\">Tap a preset to fight it straight away, or set both armies yourself first. The left side is yours — the tags below switch orders and engagement rules, and single units can be dragged. Rerun repeats the same matchup to see the spread. Exit reloads back into the normal game.</div>",
  "<div class=\"pTitle\">💾 存檔／讀檔</div>": "<div class=\"pTitle\">💾 Save / load</div>",
  "<div class=\"arenaRow\"><button id=\"saveImport\" type=\"button\">⤒ 匯入檔案</button><button id=\"saveClose\" type=\"button\">✕ 關閉</button></div>": "<div class=\"arenaRow\"><button id=\"saveImport\" type=\"button\">⤒ Import file</button><button id=\"saveClose\" type=\"button\">✕ Close</button></div>",
  "<div class=\"arenaHint\">存檔存在<b>這台裝置的瀏覽器</b>裡（不會上傳）。⚠️ iPhone/iPad 的 Safari 約 <b>7 天沒開這個網站就會自動清掉</b>——重要進度請按 <b>⤓</b> 匯出成檔案留一份（也是換裝置的方法）。讀檔＝從存檔當下接著玩。</div>": "<div class=\"arenaHint\">Saves live in <b>this browser on this device</b> and are never uploaded. ⚠️ Safari on iPhone/iPad clears them after roughly <b>7 days without visiting the site</b> — press <b>⤓</b> to export anything you want to keep (that is also how you move a game to another device). Loading resumes exactly where the save was taken.</div>",
  "<h1>⚔️ 中世紀 RTS</h1>": "<h1>⚔️ Medieval RTS</h1>",
