  "<div class=\"homeLb\">敵方文明</div><div class=\"rowBtns\" id=\"homeAiCivRow\"></div>": "<div class=\"homeLb\">Opponent civilisation</div><div class=\"rowBtns\" id=\"homeAiCivRow\"></div>",
