  "<div class=\"homeFoot\">開局後仍可用 ⚙️ 換對手、🗺 換地圖（都＝重開新局）、🔧→💾 存檔。</div>": "<div class=\"homeFoot\">In game you can still use ⚙️ to change opponent and 🗺 to change map (both start a new game), and 🔧→💾 to save.</div>",
